paragraphs.title: People spend most money on Thursdays, but make most transactions on Tuesdays
paragraphs.text:
%sql
select date_format(data ,'u') as dzien, count(1) as cnt, sum(kwota) as amt from bzwbk_p.transakcje group by date_format(data ,'u') order by dzien

%sql
select date_format(data ,'u') as dzien, count(1) as cnt, sum(kwota) as amt from bzwbk_p.transakcje group by date_format(data ,'u') order by dzien

%sql
select wiek, count(1) as liczba_klientow from bzwbk.klient where wiek is not null group by wiek

%sql
select data, sum(kwota) as kwota from bzwbk_p.transakcje group by data order by data

paragraphs.text:
%sql
SELECT
   CAST(hist.x as double) as kwota,
   CAST(hist.y as bigint) as liczba
FROM (select 
      histogram_numeric(kwota, 20) as kwota_hist
      from
      bzwbk.transakcje
      where
      kwota < 1000) a
LATERAL VIEW explode(kwota_hist) exploded_table as hist

%sql
SELECT
   CAST(hist.x as double) as saldo,
   CAST(hist.y as bigint) as liczba
FROM (select 
      histogram_numeric(saldo, 20) as saldo_hist
      from
      bzwbk.rachunek
      where produkt = 'KONTO 123') a
LATERAL VIEW explode(saldo_hist) exploded_table as hist

%sql
select produkt, count(1) as c1 from bzwbk.rachunek group by produkt order by c1 desc
